Rewrite frontend/src/components/JobCard.jsx. The card should look like a Naukri/Indeed job card. Props: { job, onClick }.

Card structure (top to bottom):
Row 1: Company logo placeholder (a square 48x48 div with the first letter of company name, background #e8f5f1, color #40826D, font-weight bold, border-radius 8px) + to the right: job title (h3, clickable, calls onClick) and company name (p, muted)
