Row 3: Category tag (small pill badge, green outline) + experience tag (show "Fresher" if salary is monthly/internship else "1-3 yrs")
Row 4: Truncated description (max 120 chars)
Row 5: Bottom bar — left: posted date formatted as "X days ago" using postedAt field (if missing show "Recently"), right: "View Details" button with className="btn-view-details"

